{"tid":2337200,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"官方宣布 YOASOBI出演紅白歌合戰，史上第一例 未出過CD就上紅白：","createTime":"2020-12-23T06:40:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-23T09:53:18.000Z","uid":60286,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ee06d7449f1a5bf9bdf94f52b65b8e00cb5d8907","tid":2337200,"uid":60286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T06:40:36.000Z","msg":"流行在走、改變要有。第71屆NHK紅白歌唱大賽將於下週四（31日）晚間登場，製作單位宣布追加男女組合「YOASOBI」，其單曲「向夜晚奔去」為今年日本最夯，不但要獻出電視演出初體驗，未發行實體CD就獲邀參加更是超級特例。<br />\n<br />\n「YOASOBI」由製作人Ayase以及主唱ikura於2019年10月組成，他們的作品都以小說為基底化為詞曲，首張單曲「夜に駆ける/向夜晚奔去」在同年12月數位上架，YouTube的MV瀏覽次數已達1.3億次，更佔據今年日本各個音樂榜冠軍數週，甚至稱霸日本Billboard年度冠軍，名符其實為2020日本樂壇年度神曲。<br />\n<br />\n出道一年發行六首數位單曲，「YOASOBI」從未在任何電視頻道表演過，而NHK紅白歌唱大賽以往都是以實體銷售數字加上當年的話題、人氣為依據提出邀約，這次花了相當長的時間才說服兩人參加，屆時會有何種表現或許可以拭目以待。"},{"pid":"01aacc0770b868fc607bf985a87b2443a8173c0e","tid":2337200,"uid":32150,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T06:46:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10351da3ed473112ab4174439a30fae166e3f0ee","tid":2337200,"uid":1130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T07:25:51.000Z","msg":"竟然未出碟就上得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"241570fa919199b2cb9b815ee14bfce1c98be70a","tid":2337200,"uid":317459,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T08:16:24.000Z","msg":"合理啦 <br />\n紅到咁到唔上既話就真係奇怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19f17e43837b7c67eacc2508af24312c2a2edd18","tid":2337200,"uid":52073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T09:13:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd05cf3e72c98c40cb66b69dc8a7a287c878872